                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-emerald-600 mr-2"></i>Minimal documentation</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-emerald-600 mr-2"></i>Expert guidance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 border-l-4 border-orange-500">
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Education Loans</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">Up to ₹10,00,000 for education.</p>
                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-emerald-600 mr-2"></i>Lower interest rates</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-emerald-600 mr-2"></i>Deferred payment options</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-emerald-600 mr-2"></i>No collateral</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
